name: sumi:(inked) *special* CURSED GOAT CARD
description: Once the herd of nubian goats were all gone, I found a little chest they seemed to be hiding. Inside of it, there was a pack of what looked like playing cards, 7 of them, all the same, showing me something I didn't suspect could exist... Now I know why the goats were trying to hide this. Super shiny and cool though.
